text: What kind of pictures are you taking?

So cute!
Do you often take pictures of cats?

Well, yeah...! But I take other stuff too,
you know. Like... things that catch my eye!

Oh, really? ...Then,
isn't it strange that you don't have any pictures of me?

Is that so?
Well then, I'd be happy to take one if you'd like!

Huh-
But shouldn't that go through the agency?
Oh, you won't let me take one, huh!
